      <title>法国兴业银行称塞地有望因高实际利率而反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/-usd-ghs-cedi-ready-for-rebound-on-high-real-rates-societe-generale-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受高利率、政府财政前景改善和黄金收益的推动，加纳塞地兑美元汇率跌至新低，有望反弹。]]></description>
