      <title>惠誉表示，巴西的投资级评级“还很低”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/brazil-s-investment-grade-is-further-down-the-road-fitch-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级表示，巴西政府需要实现财政目标、将政府债务稳定在当前水平并建立财政信誉，然后才能获得信用评分升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/brazil-s-investment-grade-is-further-down-the-road-fitch-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 14:10:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
